>ابحث</para
></entry>
</row>
<row
><entry
><para
><userinput
>u</userinput
></para
></entry>
<entry
><para
>تراجع</para
></entry>
</row>
<row
><entry
><para
><keycombo action="simul"
>&Ctrl;<keycap
>R</keycap
